WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 34=

02:13.741 --> 02:14.542
Gran...

02:15.982 --> 02:17.022
Grandfather.

02:17.501 --> 02:18.302
Grandfather.

02:24.422 --> 02:25.702
Grandfather.

02:32.822 --> 02:34.702
Don't leave me.

02:41.520 --> 02:45.990
ظآزThe moonlight had scattered some dustظآز

02:48.176 --> 02:52.824
ظآزAnd the cracks in memory were coveredظآز

02:55.120 --> 02:59.668
ظآزWhen did something chip away insideظآز

02:59.984 --> 03:06.576
ظآزIt's flickering,
as if expectations were lostظآز

03:08.880 --> 03:13.040
ظآزYou always love with painظآز

03:14.512 --> 03:19.984
ظآزForgetting you deserve to be loved tooظآز

03:22.192 --> 03:28.944
ظآزHow the rain outside
nurtures the heartظآز

03:28.944 --> 03:33.521
ظآزThat's how you are cherishedظآز

03:34.608 --> 03:37.872
ظآزYou don't need to chaseظآز

03:38.096 --> 03:41.264
ظآزAfter clouds that winds pursueظآز

03:41.520 --> 03:44.656
ظآزYou can silently watch each sunriseظآز

03:45.008 --> 03:48.048
ظآزFinding happiness by your sideظآز

03:48.400 --> 03:51.568
ظآزYou don't need to chart a mapظآز

03:51.856 --> 03:55.056
ظآزOf every bend where love winds onظآز

03:55.056 --> 03:58.512
ظآزNor travel far to guide its courseظآز

03:58.512 --> 04:01.616
ظآزTo make your heartظآز

04:02.480 --> 04:05.840
ظآزWarm againظآز

04:17.852 --> 04:19.185
(Qingshuang's Tomb)

04:19.185 --> 04:23.853
ظآزTime has kept some lines aliveظآز

04:24.688 --> 04:30.628
ظآزThey've recorded of your dreamsظآز

04:32.816 --> 04:38.424
ظآزHow the snow on the peak
buries the woundsظآز

04:39.472 --> 04:43.876
ظآزThat's how you will be trustedظآز

