ظآزWarm againظآز

05:14.670 --> 05:16.306
(Master Helai's Tomb)

05:17.744 --> 05:21.825
ظآزTime is flowing moonlightظآز

05:22.352 --> 05:24.597
ظآزTreasuring memoriesظآز

05:25.424 --> 05:28.308
ظآزYou sent out the lightظآز

05:29.232 --> 05:31.472
ظآزFrom far, far awayظآز

05:31.472 --> 05:36.052
ظآزLeaves are like broad, gentle handsظآز

05:36.052 --> 05:38.753
