07:54.702 --> 07:57.622
Silly child, why are you lying here?

07:59.981 --> 08:01.142
Grandfather.

08:02.421 --> 08:05.582
The ground is cold. Don't catch a chill.

08:06.221 --> 08:08.101
Come on. Get up.

08:32.342 --> 08:37.661
Wild monkeys often roam
the back mountain. They are fierce.

08:37.901 --> 08:40.622
Don't come here anymore.

08:43.382 --> 08:47.262
I'll stay at the academy with you.

08:48.142 --> 08:49.262
I am not going anywhere.

09:01.862 --> 09:03.862
Let's go. Don't be afraid.

09:03.862 --> 09:04.622
My lady.

09:06.541 --> 09:07.301
My lady.

09:10.022 --> 09:11.742
You scared me to death.

09:16.262 --> 09:19.181
Why did you go to the back mountain?
We were all looking for you.

09:20.262 --> 09:23.421
The red beans I planted in the house
have borne fruit. I've picked them all.

09:23.421 --> 09:27.262
Today, I'll cook them all,
so you can have some red bean rice.

09:27.421 --> 09:30.262
It's really rare
that you are being so generous.

09:30.262 --> 09:31.742
Then I'll have two bowls today.

09:31.982 --> 09:32.982
I want five bowls!

09:32.982 --> 09:33.482
Alright.

09:33.482 --> 09:33.982
- Me too.
- Me too.

09:33.982 --> 09:36.421
Let's go eat red bean rice together.

09:37.701 --> 09:39.742
Let's go together.

09:40.752 --> 09:44.080
ظآزFrom far, far awayظآز

09:44.080 --> 09:47.219
ظآزYou don't need to chaseظآز

09:47.219 --> 09:50.803
ظآزNo need to chaseظآز

09:50.803 --> 09:53.489
ظآزThat quiet and steady happinessظآز

09:53.489 --> 09:58.256
ظآزDeep in the woodsظآز

09:58.256 --> 10:04.473
(Headmaster Xu's Tomb)

10:51.622 --> 10:52.122
Li,

10:56.222 --> 10:57.462
the sun is out.

11:03.856 --> 11:07.997
ظآزYou really don't need to chaseظآز

11:08.848 --> 11:11.824
ظآزNo need to chaseظآز

11:11.824 --> 11:15.440
ظآزThat quiet and steady happinessظآز

11:16.720 --> 11:23.207
ظآزTo spend a lifetime readingظآز

11:57.982 --> 11:58.781
Your Highness.

12:13.581 --> 12:16.142
Master Feng,
thank you for your hard work.

12:23.982 --> 12:26.541
Is it the season for snowing?

12:26.960 --> 12:30.576
(Suixue Pass)

12:55.661 --> 12:57.502
It's cold in the north. Put this on.

13:06.821 --> 13:07.661
Brother.

13:11.781 --> 13:12.742
Let's go.

13:16.622 --> 13:18.382
Actually, I know what you want to say.

13:20.262 --> 13:22.181
Before, I didn't know
where I wanted to go

13:23.982 --> 13:25.502
until I met Ye Li.

13:27.382 --> 13:30.102
I said I owe her two lives,
and I must repay her.

13:31.821 --> 13:35.222
At first, I didn't know
where I wanted to go either.

13:36.222 --> 13:39.581
I thought it was nice
to just stick with her.

13:40.622 --> 13:42.181
But later I found out

13:44.222 --> 13:45.342
this kind of life

13:47.102 --> 13:48.342
is so wonderful.

13:49.821 --> 13:53.742
When the sun rises,
I'd get up and clean the shop,

13:55.821 --> 13:56.781
greet the customers,

13:58.781 --> 14:00.222
bargain with them,

14:01.581 --> 14:04.262
eat and sleep with others,

14:06.142 --> 14:09.541
fight over meat in the dishes
and share half a flatbread with them.

14:43.742 --> 14:44.541
Brother.

14:48.821 --> 14:50.701
Can we really live this kind of life?

14:54.982 --> 14:56.102
I don't want anything.

14:56.421 --> 14:58.181
I'm not afraid
of hardship or exhaustion.

14:58.462 --> 15:00.222
I'm fine with hauling goods all day.

15:01.301 --> 15:02.502
And I don't eat much.

15:02.502 --> 15:03.941
I don't need a big mansion.

15:08.502 --> 15:09.661
It's all my fault.

15:11.701 --> 15:12.581
You should go.

15:19.061 --> 15:19.901
I should go?

15:21.821 --> 15:23.781
And let Mo Jingli kill you?

15:29.382 --> 15:30.541
I don't care.

15:32.622 --> 15:33.901
Even if you have to die,

15:34.661 --> 15:36.342
why not try once?

15:37.262 --> 15:38.581
Because of Su Zuidie?

15:39.382 --> 15:41.262
She killed many innocent people,

15:42.022 --> 15:46.061
just to seek revenge
and to regain what belonged to her.

15:47.022 --> 15:49.102
I've heard these words
hundreds of times.

15:51.742 --> 15:52.941
But

15:54.502 --> 15:55.742
that's what she wanted.

15:57.421 --> 16:01.821
If seeking a life of luxury
requires us to take such a path,

16:02.982 --> 16:04.262
I'd rather give it up.

16:06.622 --> 16:08.421
I'd rather die right now.

16:28.622 --> 16:29.421
Brother.

16:52.742 --> 16:53.901
Let me take you away.

17:39.056 --> 17:42.192
(Map of Defense Mansion)

17:46.821 --> 17:49.502
Your Highness,
I received news from the capital.

17:49.621 --> 17:51.341
Marquis Muyang has died in prison.

17:53.581 --> 17:54.381
As expected.

17:55.381 --> 17:58.742
Actually, I'm quite surprised
that he could live that long.

17:59.861 --> 18:01.341
Qin Cang has been sentenced to exile.

18:01.462 --> 18:03.621
Zhou Tianyang escorted the coffin
back to his hometown.

18:03.621 --> 18:05.942
What about Li? Any news?

18:07.821 --> 18:11.581
Lady Ye has left Prince Ding's Mansion
and returned to Lishan Mountain.

18:12.541 --> 18:15.462
Back to Lishan Mountain? Why?

18:16.541 --> 18:17.742
I don't know either.

18:19.702 --> 18:22.702
What about Prince Ding? What did he do?

18:23.381 --> 18:26.942
When the news arrived, there was no word
of any unusual movement from Prince Ding.

18:42.384 --> 18:44.784
The General's Mansion at Suixue Pass
is structurally complex

18:44.784 --> 18:45.982
and heavily guarded.

18:47.182 --> 18:49.902
It is indeed extremely difficult
to sneak in without a detailed map.

18:51.982 --> 18:55.141
Painter Feng, thank you
for your hard work over all these years.

19:05.968 --> 19:10.547
(Defense Mansion)

19:59.664 --> 20:01.680
(Defense Mansion)

20:26.288 --> 20:29.648
(Wude Residence)

21:58.896 --> 22:05.808
(Deep Contemplation)

22:07.921 --> 22:11.857
ظآزThose fallen into the abyssظآز

22:15.024 --> 22:17.320
(Deep Contemplation)

22:17.849 --> 22:19.040
(Mastery of Heaven and Earth)

22:19.040 --> 22:26.129
ظآزIf you treat pain as swallowed needlesظآز

22:27.601 --> 22:38.008
ظآزThe scars etched
sharpen the heart to a bladeظآز

22:38.827 --> 22:41.908
(Headmaster Xu's Tomb)

22:42.608 --> 22:43.739
(Minglun Hall)

22:48.170 --> 22:53.712
ظآزFollow me, debts unpaid, march onظآز

22:53.712 --> 22:56.938
(Clarify Truth and Uphold Orthodox)

22:57.872 --> 23:01.584
ظآزCast into despairظآز

23:04.240 --> 23:06.224
(Master Zhu's Tomb)

23:07.312 --> 23:11.760
ظآزI would rather drain our hopeظآز

23:11.905 --> 23:17.456
ظآزThan survive temporarily for illusionsظآز

23:17.456 --> 23:20.127
(Maintain Reverence
and Investigate Principles)

23:20.127 --> 23:22.134
(Langhan Pavilion)

23:35.778 --> 23:37.839
(Astronomy)

23:48.942 --> 23:53.961
(Astronomy)

24:01.520 --> 24:06.844
(Mastery of Heaven and Earth)

24:26.128 --> 24:31.408
(Lishan Academy)

24:31.408 --> 24:34.846
ظآزThe lie will finally fall apartظآز

24:36.208 --> 24:39.684
ظآزWho hides in the shadowsظآز

24:40.080 --> 24:48.918
ظآزReveal the world's true faceظآز

24:49.232 --> 24:53.232
ظآزThe living, the deadظآز

24:53.232 --> 24:57.314
ظآزToo many innocentsظآز

24:57.341 --> 24:58.262
You may leave.

24:59.022 --> 24:59.821
Your Majesty.

25:02.141 --> 25:04.702
Your Majesty,
here's a report from Lishan Mountain.

25:11.061 --> 25:14.061
(Total of 47 members of Lishan Academy,
including masters and scholars,)

25:14.061 --> 25:15.262
(suffered from the disease.)

25:15.262 --> 25:16.821
(Neither medicine nor prayer worked.)

25:16.821 --> 25:17.902
(All have perished,)

25:18.101 --> 25:20.902
(except Princess Ding.)

25:21.182 --> 25:25.222
(I was shocked to hear this,
thus report to Your Majesty.)

25:29.341 --> 25:30.502
Is the news true?

25:31.781 --> 25:35.462
Last night, Gongshu Yang's urgent report
was already submitted to Her Majesty.

25:35.982 --> 25:37.022
At noon today,

25:37.141 --> 25:39.371
memorials from the local prefectures,
governors,

25:39.371 --> 25:41.742
and garrison troops of Lishan Mountain
also arrived.

25:42.182 --> 25:43.222
After verifications,

25:43.301 --> 25:49.141
all 47 members of Lishan Academy
have perished, except Princess Ding.

25:50.182 --> 25:52.902
Over forty people,
and only one survived?

25:53.061 --> 25:55.942
It is said that three years
after Lishan Mountain was sealed off,

25:56.262 --> 25:58.101
the scholars
contracted an acute illness.

25:58.301 --> 25:59.821
The disease came fiercely.

26:00.141 --> 26:04.422
Dozens of scholars lived and ate together,
and soon everyone fell ill.

26:05.262 --> 26:07.861
Wasn't the famous physician
Master Helai also in there?

26:08.341 --> 26:10.022
One can't make something out of nothing.

26:10.662 --> 26:13.101
At that time, Lishan Mountain
had exhausted all supplies.

26:13.101 --> 26:16.982
They barely had enough food and water,
how could they have enough herbs?

26:17.702 --> 26:19.621
Lishan Academy is remarkable.

26:20.101 --> 26:23.502
Trapped in such a desperate situation,
yet they still upheld their justice,

26:23.821 --> 26:25.462
refusing to open the gate until death.

26:26.301 --> 26:29.702
People of Lishan Mountain
are all loyal and righteous.

26:30.422 --> 26:33.781
It's truly a pity
they met such a pathetic end.

26:45.902 --> 26:50.341
Your Majesty, Lishan Academy
is the cultural root of Dachu.

26:50.502 --> 26:53.341
It has influenced countless generations
of scholars over the millennium.

26:53.462 --> 26:55.088
Even after eight years of being sealed,

26:55.088 --> 26:58.462
it remains the foundation
of Dachu's cultural heritage.

26:58.821 --> 27:02.662
Once the tragic news spreads,
the people will surely be shocked.

27:03.101 --> 27:08.182
The masters who wrote books
were trapped in Lishan Mountain,

27:08.262 --> 27:10.702
preferring to die
upholding their justice.

27:11.101 --> 27:13.422
Renowned scholars from all over
will surely mourn them.

27:13.422 --> 27:16.022
And the common people will also
pay homage to Lishan Mountain.

27:16.101 --> 27:18.141
Then, grief will surge like a tide,

27:18.141 --> 27:19.422
and public sentiment will boil.

27:19.662 --> 27:23.902
You only need to offer a little guidance,
or stir things up behind the scenes,

27:23.942 --> 27:26.301
and everything
will inevitably rush towards

27:26.301 --> 27:29.662
the one who forced Lishan Mountain
to seal itself off.

27:34.462 --> 27:38.742
Provoking public sentiment
is like triggering mountain torrents.

27:39.101 --> 27:41.022
It's easy to start, but hard to stop.

27:41.422 --> 27:43.042
Back then, it was Lishan Mountain

27:43.042 --> 27:45.621
that requested to seal itself off
for compiling texts.

27:46.821 --> 27:50.781
The people know very well
why Lishan Mountain sealed itself off.

27:51.462 --> 27:55.821
Compiling texts was merely
an excuse to cover up the truth.

27:56.821 --> 27:58.301
Once the tragic news gets out,

27:58.301 --> 28:01.702
the truth suppressed for years
will finally come to light.

28:01.702 --> 28:06.381
The people will surely recall the reason
why Lishan Mountain sealed itself off.

28:07.381 --> 28:11.502
Headmaster Xu Qingyun of Lishan Mountain
had always upheld the orthodoxy,

28:11.662 --> 28:15.541
and been loyal to the Mo Dynasty,
which means loyal to Your Majesty.

28:15.902 --> 28:19.222
Therefore, no matter
how turbulent public sentiment becomes,

28:19.262 --> 28:22.141
Your Majesty will always
have the upper hand.

28:24.381 --> 28:27.902
In the past six months,
Mother gradually returned the power to me

28:28.341 --> 28:30.141
and taught me how to reign the nation.

28:30.821 --> 28:33.742
After Marquis Muyang's execution,
she missed several morning courts.

28:34.262 --> 28:36.821
I think
she has lost intentions to reign now.

28:39.022 --> 28:43.061
Your Majesty,
you will come of age next year.

28:43.182 --> 28:45.242
It won't be too late for us
to make plans

28:45.242 --> 28:47.942
if Her Majesty still hasn't
returned her power by then.

28:50.902 --> 28:52.061
That makes sense.

28:53.982 --> 28:57.262
Your Majesty, you taking over the nation
is what the people desire.

28:57.422 --> 28:59.502
Yet you have waited year after year,

29:00.022 --> 29:03.022
from your youth to your coming of age.

29:03.821 --> 29:07.341
If next year Her Majesty
still refuses to hand over the power,

29:07.662 --> 29:09.341
will you wait until you are thirty?

29:09.902 --> 29:13.581
By then, will there still be
an opportunity like this?

29:13.702 --> 29:14.502
But...

29:19.462 --> 29:21.432
But I have just started
handling state affairs,

29:21.432 --> 29:22.861
and my foundation is still shallow.

29:23.462 --> 29:24.861
Without Mother's support...

29:27.942 --> 29:32.381
Your Majesty,
loyal and righteous men abound in Dachu.

29:32.861 --> 29:34.742
Civil officials offer advice
with tablets,

29:34.742 --> 29:36.381
and military officials fight
with swords.

29:36.462 --> 29:37.902
All the officials in court

29:37.902 --> 29:41.662
and the common people
respect the late emperor.

29:42.141 --> 29:45.022
Now that Your Majesty
has inherited the throne,

29:45.061 --> 29:47.662
bearing the mandate of heaven
and winning the people's hearts,

29:47.662 --> 29:49.502
why fear the power of others?

29:49.502 --> 29:52.942
And why rely on others' support?

30:05.462 --> 30:08.422
T-This is not a natural disaster,

30:08.702 --> 30:10.061
but actually a man-made calamity.

30:10.422 --> 30:11.581
It's not about the disease,

30:12.262 --> 30:13.781
but the vile scheme.

30:14.422 --> 30:18.320
T-The Empress Dowager Guo,

30:18.320 --> 30:20.022
relying on
the late emperor's benevolence,

30:23.902 --> 30:28.861
h-has usurped the power of the throne
and made arbitrary decisions,

30:29.022 --> 30:30.462
stealing the light of the emperor.

30:32.022 --> 30:32.982
Please calm your anger.

30:33.861 --> 30:34.662
Who wrote this?

30:35.781 --> 30:41.861
Your Majesty, this is an anonymous poem
circulating among the people.

30:42.022 --> 30:45.262
I do not know who wrote it.

30:45.662 --> 30:47.541
These people are utterly absurd!

30:48.101 --> 30:50.861
Forming private societies
and gathering crowds is a serious crime.

30:50.861 --> 30:52.821
How dare they write such a treasonous,

30:52.942 --> 30:54.341
slanderous poem against Mother!

30:54.341 --> 30:55.341
They deserve death.

30:56.101 --> 30:57.022
In my opinion,

30:57.541 --> 31:01.061
such rebellious people should be arrested
and thrown into prison immediately.

31:01.301 --> 31:03.341
Punish them severely without mercy
to warn others.

31:06.141 --> 31:08.781
Your Majesties, please calm down.

31:09.742 --> 31:12.101
Lishan Academy holds
a cultural lineage of a thousand years.

31:12.462 --> 31:15.182
Suddenly hearing the tragic news
of the entire academy's demise,

31:15.422 --> 31:16.541
the scholars are in shock,

31:16.541 --> 31:17.702
and the people are in grief.

31:18.222 --> 31:20.621
Out of a moment of rage,
some ignorant scholars

31:21.262 --> 31:23.141
may have acted
or spoken inappropriately.

31:23.662 --> 31:27.781
Once this wave of grief passes,
people will naturally calm down.

31:29.008 --> 31:30.896
Lishan Mountain
has suffered such calamity.

31:31.341 --> 31:34.222
The court shares the sorrow.

31:35.621 --> 31:38.821
If they want to pay homage
to Lishan Mountain, then let them go.

31:39.101 --> 31:43.502
The court should not obstruct them,
and should show empathy for them.

31:44.462 --> 31:47.902
Order the Ministry of Rites
to immediately dispatch capable officers,

31:48.101 --> 31:50.942
carrying the court's rewards
and condolences,

31:51.182 --> 31:53.341
to head to Lishan Mountain
to offer sacrifices,

31:54.101 --> 31:56.801
to mourn the deceased
and comfort the living

31:56.801 --> 31:58.182
on behalf of the court.

32:05.061 --> 32:10.101
Your Majesties, in my opinion,
the key of the poem

32:10.101 --> 32:13.621
circulating among the people
is not about mourning.

32:17.341 --> 32:21.391
Instead, they want you to follow
the will of heaven and the people,

32:21.391 --> 32:23.301
to return power to His Majesty.

32:29.541 --> 32:31.341
I make bold to petition.

32:31.902 --> 32:34.502
At this time
of surging public sentiment,

32:34.942 --> 32:39.742
why not take advantage of the situation
and return power to His Majesty?

32:46.301 --> 32:47.101
How dare you!

32:47.982 --> 32:52.061
I am still young and inexperienced,
in need of Mother's advice and guidance.

32:58.861 --> 33:02.621
Your Majesty, in recent months,
imperial physicians have repeatedly advised

33:03.022 --> 33:04.942
that the Empress Dowager
has no appetite...

33:04.942 --> 33:05.742
- Enough!
- She...

33:15.902 --> 33:16.742
Mother.

33:18.502 --> 33:21.061
The temporary palace in Fuchang County
on the capital outskirts

33:21.061 --> 33:21.982
has hot springs

33:21.982 --> 33:22.902
and serene scenery,

33:22.902 --> 33:23.902
perfect for recuperation.

33:24.982 --> 33:26.381
Once this turmoil subsides,

33:26.942 --> 33:29.342
I will personally lead the civil
and military officials

33:29.342 --> 33:31.262
to respectfully
welcome your return to court.

33:34.022 --> 33:36.902
His Majesty's benevolence and filial piety
are witnessed by all.

33:42.541 --> 33:44.541
Your Majesty, you can rest
and recuperate in peace.

33:44.702 --> 33:46.022
When your health is restored,

33:46.182 --> 33:49.272
you can witness with your own eyes
the prosperity of Dachu

33:49.272 --> 33:50.581
under His Majesty's rule.

33:50.861 --> 33:53.141
Isn't that wonderful?

34:11.141 --> 34:12.342
Do you all

34:13.741 --> 34:15.342
think so?

34:23.181 --> 34:25.701
For the sake of Your Majesty's health,

34:26.822 --> 34:29.902
we earnestly request you to move
to the temporary palace for recuperation.

34:30.342 --> 34:33.022
All state affairs can be
entrusted to His Majesty.

34:33.541 --> 34:34.902
- I second that.
- I second that.

34:36.181 --> 34:37.541
- I second that.
- I second that.

34:37.942 --> 34:40.382
- I second that.
- I second that.

34:40.741 --> 34:42.822
- I second that.
- I second that.

35:05.168 --> 35:07.632
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

35:32.581 --> 35:33.382
You're up.

35:35.342 --> 35:38.581
The morning breeze is chilly.
Why didn't you put on more clothes?

35:39.342 --> 35:42.101
If you catch a cold, you'll suffer then.

35:43.502 --> 35:44.621
It's not chilly inside.

35:51.261 --> 35:52.701
The windows are still open.

35:55.141 --> 35:56.862
If I feel cold, I'll close them.

35:57.862 --> 35:58.701
Don't worry.

36:08.342 --> 36:09.541
I got news from the palace.

36:10.101 --> 36:11.661
It says the Empress Dowager is unwell,

36:12.502 --> 36:15.536
preparing to move to the temporary palace
in Fuchang County for recuperation.

36:17.661 --> 36:18.741
His Majesty issued an edict

36:19.181 --> 36:21.462
to clear the name of Lishan Academy,

36:23.302 --> 36:24.880
and compensate the bereaved families.

36:26.902 --> 36:27.701
Is that so?

36:29.661 --> 36:30.502
You anticipated it?

36:38.822 --> 36:39.661
This is...

36:41.942 --> 36:42.782
My secret.

36:44.221 --> 36:47.181
Why left such a secret here like this?

36:50.302 --> 36:52.181
Some have already become the past.

36:53.661 --> 36:54.782
While some...

37:01.661 --> 37:03.462
There were four of these straw dolls.

37:04.982 --> 37:06.261
Lu Changfu,

37:06.782 --> 37:07.862
the Ye family,

37:08.822 --> 37:09.902
Marquis Muyang,

37:12.101 --> 37:13.181
and the fourth one...

37:14.942 --> 37:16.022
Who is it?

37:24.661 --> 37:25.541
You've guessed it?

37:26.701 --> 37:27.502
Empress Dowager.

37:30.862 --> 37:32.661
Starting from the fire
in the Eastern Palace,

37:33.701 --> 37:35.221
to the late emperor's decree,

37:36.502 --> 37:38.462
and then the sealing of Lishan Mountain.

37:39.422 --> 37:44.181
Every single one of these
was to pave the way for her.

37:46.982 --> 37:51.101
For eight years,
Marquis Muyang framed loyal subjects,

37:51.902 --> 37:53.181
abused torture,

37:54.502 --> 37:55.741
and controlled the court.

37:56.741 --> 38:01.181
Without her approval and indulgence,
how could he be so rampant?

38:03.061 --> 38:04.661
Marquis Muyang has been executed,

38:06.141 --> 38:10.581
but she is still
the mighty Empress Dowager,

38:12.541 --> 38:16.701
unstained and unburdened
by any dirty deeds.

38:24.822 --> 38:28.261
- Li.
- I understand what you want to say.

38:29.621 --> 38:31.382
Even if I still hold my resentment,

38:32.822 --> 38:34.541
I won't act rashly.

38:48.302 --> 38:49.902
The blood on her hands

38:51.221 --> 38:53.741
will not dry up
with the passage of time.

38:55.181 --> 38:56.621
The wails of those lost souls

38:57.661 --> 39:00.822
will one day penetrate the palace walls.

39:21.902 --> 39:24.541
Only such a phoenix crown
is worthy of you.

39:25.382 --> 39:26.992
With phoenix crown and ceremonial robe,

39:27.101 --> 39:28.302
you are the model for all.

39:29.342 --> 39:32.462
Jin, you've finally achieved your wish.

39:36.181 --> 39:37.141
Wanzhou.

39:38.661 --> 39:41.621
(Wanzhou, General Mo won't return
to the capital without a decree.)

39:42.022 --> 39:44.061
(Think of a way. We must save him.)

39:44.862 --> 39:48.382
You told me to get the decree.
You said you would save him.

39:48.541 --> 39:49.982
Jin, you lied to me.

39:52.880 --> 39:55.101
You ordered Marquis Muyang
to burn the Eastern Palace,

39:55.101 --> 39:57.382
obtained the decree
to frame Prince Ding's Mansion,

39:57.822 --> 40:02.382
sealed off Lishan Mountain,
and killed everyone standing in your way.

40:02.581 --> 40:06.181
Your path is stained
with schemes and blood.

40:06.701 --> 40:07.902
But now?

40:08.382 --> 40:10.621
Everyone has left you.
Even your son has betrayed you.

40:10.982 --> 40:12.141
No.

40:12.661 --> 40:15.101
Why are you...? Why?

40:16.942 --> 40:20.261
(We earnestly request you to move
to the temporary palace for recuperation.)

40:20.541 --> 40:23.221
All state affairs can be
entrusted to His Majesty.

40:23.741 --> 40:25.101
- I second that.
- I second that.

40:26.502 --> 40:28.101
- I second that.
- I second that.

40:28.862 --> 40:29.776
(I, Guo Jin,)

40:30.288 --> 40:32.982
(was once the most outstanding scholar
of Lishan Academy.)

40:33.744 --> 40:37.502
(I once wanted to stand firm
between heaven and earth like a man,)

40:37.502 --> 40:39.061
(to leave my mark in this world.)

40:40.022 --> 40:44.502
(Yet I had to be worn down
in endless palace intrigues.)

40:45.422 --> 40:47.862
(I didn't accept it.
I refused to accept it.)

40:48.181 --> 40:50.621
(If this world does not
allow women to be strong,)

40:51.261 --> 40:53.661
(I will change the rules of this world
with my own hands.)

40:53.661 --> 40:55.342
Are all traces thoroughly erased?

40:56.342 --> 40:59.902
(Even if rivers of blood
flow beneath my feet.)

41:00.240 --> 41:02.096
The post of Chief Minister
of Imperial Court...

41:02.942 --> 41:05.502
Naturally, you'll be
the one to take on this post.

41:07.141 --> 41:08.502
By Her Majesty's orders,

41:09.581 --> 41:12.382
Lishan Academy
seals itself off to compile texts.

41:12.382 --> 41:16.502
From today, elite imperial guards
are to be dispatched to guard it

41:16.782 --> 41:19.382
and block all key passes and roads
to Lishan Mountain.

41:20.621 --> 41:23.061
You abducted the crown prince's son.

41:23.061 --> 41:24.422
Seize them!

41:34.462 --> 41:37.541
There are just a few of them.
How dare they try to stop the tide

41:37.541 --> 41:41.221
and obstruct Her Majesty's ascension?
They deserve to die.

41:42.800 --> 41:43.856
(Death)

41:50.982 --> 41:52.181
Mom.

42:21.701 --> 42:23.741
Do you know where Xu Wanzhou is buried?

42:26.261 --> 42:28.701
I heard she is buried
in Zhengyi Temple outside the city.

42:30.061 --> 42:31.540
Would Your Majesty like to visit?

42:31.540 --> 42:34.352
(Preview)

42:34.822 --> 42:36.581
If I had known hiring
would be so difficult,

42:36.621 --> 42:38.741
we should not have let Wei Zhuang go.

42:39.061 --> 42:42.141
He's an official now,
with a bright future ahead.

42:42.382 --> 42:43.502
You mean Tang Zixiao?

42:43.942 --> 42:46.022
I fear he harbors mischief
and means ill.

42:46.022 --> 42:47.502
With a theft record.

42:47.862 --> 42:51.022
He was released from Jingzhao prison
last twelfth month.

42:51.942 --> 42:53.261
You seem to like him quite a bit.

42:54.741 --> 42:57.061
You come to my place every day,
and I welcome you.

42:57.061 --> 43:00.181
But you can't just hang around
with all sorts of shady characters here.

43:00.208 --> 43:02.422
Whose fault is it that your shop
is full of such people?

43:02.422 --> 43:04.902
I overheard that Commander
of Suixue Pass was killed,

43:04.902 --> 43:06.141
and Uncle Xiuyao is going.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhileظآز

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
ظآزTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadowظآز

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through timeظآز

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your paceظآز

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
ظآزUnbound by formظآز
